div.p:
“I know you do, strange being. The coarse fare, the mushrooms and the unflavoured
                    water, you make your chosen diet in a palace. You dispense with our luxuries;
                    you—you even like work.”

But Brekekex jumped up and said hotly “I won’t have it. He isn’t married himself;
                    and he may make out he has married her in earnest and claim the Kingdom of
                    Grachidichika for himself in right of her.”
